article_id:781,category_name:Important,title_name:Shop Maintenance[Update],image_path:,message:<div>The Shop will be undergoing maintenance during the following period. All features other than the Shop will be playable during this time.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>■Maintenance Period:</div><div>From <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570003200"></span> to when the maintenance is completed.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>■Details:</div><div>We will be changing the price of in-game items following an increase in the Japanese consumption tax rate.</div><div>This change will only affect users whose country is set to Japan in the store settings.</div><div><br></div><div>&nbsp;■Issues Regarding Shop Maintenance<br>We have confirmed that the following issues were occurring during the shop maintenance.<br>・Reaching 0 HP during a quest while not having enough diamantium to purchase a continue will cause the game to freeze.<br>・Depending on the Shop button&#39;s status, the stamina/getherwing recovery pop-up accessible from the top of the screen may not display correctly.<br>・In some cases, it&#39;s impossible to recover stamina and getherwings with anything other than recovery items, even when having enough diamantium or wyrmite to do so.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(44, 130, 201);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570012200"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>Shop maintenance has been finished as of <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1570012200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1569987900,update_time1570012297